          "reviewBody": "This is the most tribal school I ever visited. The study are same as other school even other school provide you better study with low fees and facilities as compared to this school . I am complaining from 1 year about the Ac ( there is no Ac in students class room ) and there is response regarding this . One thing they did is increased fees annually and the infrastructure remain same . The one who enjoy with your is staff members and the high authority people. So if u have money to waste so u must go in this school",
