          "reviewBody": "As per the study point Scholl is good as other school but in terms of facilities they provide to your wards is poor ,because they increase there fess every time but facilities which they must provide like ac in classes are not fulfil , the staff members or teachers etc were sitting in ac rooms doing  there work they not even think even from student side that they also need AC rooms and all same as the staff require because student not able focus on there study , every time stickness around them , even my wards are studying in this school and it been a year I was complaining about Ac and result is they increasing the fess not resolving the issue.  children are also human being they also need those facilities which there staff getting. So the conclusion is if u have money to waste then u r welcome to go in this Scholl otherwise in this much of fees u may get same study but more facilities then this school.\nI hope amity school take this review as concern and instead of making it correct must work on there probleams",
          "publisher": {
