            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "While it's practically impossible to put a \"review\" of a place you've cherished for 14 years, just thought I'll chime in some of my beautiful experiences from this place.\nAmity indeed provides a holistic exposure to its students. There are events and competitions for everything starting from sports, to expressive arts, to even science, commerce and humanities. One can easily find various opportunities to discover their true calling here, and even hone their skills while at it. No review of the teachers, because I am not in a place to review the ones who have made me literate and educated enough to put reviews on social media platforms. Although, rest assured, the teachers here become our guardians and a parent figure in our life, for life.",
